ic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/43268/', '', 'Pertuzumab, Olaparib, Rucaparib, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Tazemetostat, Altretamine, Enasidenib, Belzutifan, Mitotane, More', 'Oprelvekin, Elapegademase, Histamine, Aldesleukin, Pegademase, Glatiramer', 1767369485);
